<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Carrinho - Dr. Derm</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .page-header {
            background: var(--gradient);
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cart-container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: -40px auto 0;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        .cart-item {
            background: white;
            padding: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 24px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .cart-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .cart-item img {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }
        .item-info {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .item-info h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }
        .item-info .brand {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .item-info .price {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        .item-controls {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        .quantity-display {
            background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        .subtotal {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }
        .cart-summary {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            position: sticky;
            top: 100px;
        }
        .summary-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 16px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .summary-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        .free-shipping {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .empty-cart {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 40px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
        }
        .empty-cart i {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }
        .empty-cart h3 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }
        .empty-cart p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }
        .checkout-btn {
            background: var(--gradient);
            color: white;
            padding: 18px 32px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }
        .checkout-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
        }
        .professional-notice {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .professional-notice i {
            color: #ef4444;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .professional-notice p {
            color: #ef4444;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .cart-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 400px;
            gap: 40px;
            align-items: start;
        }
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .cart-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 24px;
            }
            .cart-summary {
                position: static;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .cart-item {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 24px;
            }
            .item-controls {
                flex-direction: row;
                width: 100%;
                justify-content: space-between;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="main-header">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header-content">
                <div class="logo">
                    <img src="/logo dr derm.png" alt="Dr. Derm" class="logo-img">
                </div>
                
                <nav class="main-nav">
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/">Início</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/produtos">Produtos</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/sobre">Sobre</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
                
                <div class="header-actions">
                    <div class="search-box">
                        <form action="/produtos" method="GET">
                            <input type="text" name="search" placeholder="Buscar produtos...">
                            <button type="submit"><i class="fas fa-search"></i></button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="user-menu">
                        <% if (user) { %>
                            <a href="/dashboard" class="user-link">
                                <i class="fas fa-user"></i> <%= user.nome %>
                            </a>
                            <a href="/logout" class="logout-link">Sair</a>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <a href="/login" class="login-link">
                                <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Entrar
                            </a>
                            <a href="/cadastro" class="register-link">Cadastrar</a>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="cart-icon">
                        <a href="/carrinho">
                            <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i>
                            <span class="cart-count" id="cart-count"><%= cartCount || 0 %></span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1><i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i> Carrinho de Compras</h1>
            <p>Revise seus produtos antes de finalizar a compra</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="cart-container">
                <% if (items.length === 0) { %>
                    <div class="empty-cart">
                        <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i>
                        <h3>Seu carrinho está vazio</h3>
                        <p>Que tal explorar nossos produtos profissionais?</p>
                        <a href="/produtos" class="btn-primary">
                            <i class="fas fa-box-open"></i>
                            Explorar Produtos
                        </a>
                    </div>
                <% } else { %>
                    <div class="cart-grid">
                        <div class="cart-items">
                            <% items.forEach(item => { %>
                                <div class="cart-item">
                                    <img src="#" alt="<%= item.nome %>" onerror="this.src='/images/products/default.svg'">
                                    
                                    <div class="item-info">
                                        <h3><%= item.nome %></h3>
                                        <p class="brand"><%= item.marca %> - <%= item.modelo %></p>
                                        <div class="price">R$ <%= item.preco.toFixed(2).replace('.', ',') %></div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div class="item-controls">
                                        <div class="quantity-display">
                                            <i class="fas fa-box"></i>
                                            <%= item.quantidade %> un.
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="subtotal">
                                            R$ <%= item.subtotal.toFixed(2).replace('.', ',') %>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            <% }) %>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="cart-summary">
                            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 24px; color: var(--text-primary);">
                                <i class="fas fa-receipt"></i> Resumo do Pedido
                            </h3>
                            
                            <div class="summary-row">
                                <span>Subtotal (<%= items.length %> item<%= items.length > 1 ? 's' : '' %>):</span>
                                <span>R$ <%= total.toFixed(2).replace('.', ',') %></span>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="summary-row">
                                <span>Frete:</span>
                                <span class="free-shipping">
                                    <i class="fas fa-truck"></i>
                                    GRÁTIS
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="summary-row">
                                <span>Total:</span>
                                <span>R$ <%= total.toFixed(2).replace('.', ',') %></span>
                            </div>
                            
                            <% if (user && user.conselho_classe) { %>
                                <button class="checkout-btn" onclick="window.location.href='/checkout'">
                                    <i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i>
                                    Finalizar Compra
                                </button>
                                
                                <div style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 16px; background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1); border-radius: 12px; text-align: center;">
                                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt" style="color: var(--accent); margin-right: 8px;"></i>
                                    <small style="color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500;">
                                        Compra segura e exclusiva para profissionais
                                    </small>
                                </div>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <div class="professional-notice">
                                    <i class="fas fa-user-md"></i>
                                    <p>É necessário fazer login como profissional de saúde para finalizar a compra.</p>
                                    <a href="/login" class="btn-primary">
                                        <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i>
                                        Fazer Login
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                            <% } %>
                            
                            <div style="margin-top: 24px; text-align: center;">
                                <a href="/produtos" style="color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;">
                                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
                                    Continuar Comprando
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="main-footer">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>Dr. Derm</h3>
                    <p>Produtos profissionais para estética e botox, exclusivos para profissionais de saúde certificados.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h4>Links Úteis</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/produtos"><i class="fas fa-box"></i> Produtos</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/sobre"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Sobre Nós</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/termos"><i class="fas fa-file-contract"></i> Termos de Uso</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h4>Formas de Pagamento</h4>
                    <div class="payment-methods">
                        <i class="fab fa-pix" title="PIX"></i>
                        <i class="fas fa-credit-card" title="Cartão de Crédito"></i>
                        <i class="fas fa-university" title="Transferência Bancária"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h4>Contato</h4>
                    <p><i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> WhatsApp: (11) 99396-7438</p>
                    <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> contato@drderm.com.br</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>&copy; 2024 Dr. Derm. Todos os direitos reservados. | Produtos exclusivos para profissionais de saúde</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
    
    <a href="https://wa.me/5511993967438?text=Oi%2C%20gostaria%20de%20um%20produto%20ou%20um%20auxilio." class="whatsapp-float" target="_blank" title="Fale conosco no WhatsApp">
        <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i>
    </a>

    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>